<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Travel Korea - Immersive Visuals</title>
  {{>partials/head-assets}}
</head>
<body class="page-body-selection-shell">
  {{>partials/header}}

<div class="main-index-div-01">
<div class="main-index-div-02">
<img alt="Korean Landscape" class="media-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDeKSpjHsruIIaA1cmps46qV3qk2cZl3nTsF_dYGOtxJSis6DdsyZ9VcYq2VsjyeV5r59ZhxXMjknLpTAEmn1f753RifJdzHV0BFVaxGmXN39RWDaLS13VEy_6dF7W9RWsH7WqaXJI2xbEYci2DmUq5h3LR4PhlLs8WhWqggW8OsWKX7gNssRiG8w5BTFhACN4knAFtLg-URZPRkOig8Ab85bG_Xq1m3AULDUZvns7Bi8C7rgNe25wxxuyIENowYp-KRnlfoVqgSx4"/>
<div class="main-index-div-03"></div>
</div>
<div class="hero-shell">
<div class="chatbot-demo-div-02">
<h1 class="main-index-h1-01">
                어디로 떠나시나요?
            </h1>
<p class="main-index-p-01">
                여행 지역을 선택하고 숙소와 관광지를 한 번에 찾아보세요.
            </p>
</div>
<div class="hero-feature-card">
<form class="main-index-form-01" action="/bookings/map-detail" method="get">
<div class="main-index-div-04">
<div class="main-index-div-05">
<label class="label-caps-xs" for="region">광역시/도</label>
<div class="fx-group-rel">
<div class="input-icon-left">
<span class="icon-ms-muted-focus-primary">location_on</span>
</div>
<select class="main-index-select-01" id="region" name="region" required>
<option disabled="" selected="" value="">지역을 선택하세요</option>
<option value="seoul">서울특별시</option>
<option value="busan">부산광역시</option>
<option value="daegu">대구광역시</option>
<option value="incheon">인천광역시</option>
<option value="gwangju">광주광역시</option>
<option value="daejeon">대전광역시</option>
<option value="ulsan">울산광역시</option>
<option value="sejong">세종특별자치시</option>
<option value="gyeonggi">경기도</option>
<option value="gangwon">강원특별자치도</option>
<option value="chungbuk">충청북도</option>
<option value="chungnam">충청남도</option>
<option value="jeonbuk">전라북도</option>
<option value="jeonnam">전라남도</option>
<option value="gyeongbuk">경상북도</option>
<option value="gyeongnam">경상남도</option>
<option value="jeju">제주특별자치도</option>
</select>
<div class="main-index-div-06">
<span class="icon-ms-muted">expand_more</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="main-index-div-07">
<div class="stack-gap-1-5">
<label class="label-caps-xs" for="startDate">가는 날</label>
<div class="fx-group-rel">
<div class="input-icon-left">
<span class="icon-ms-muted-focus-primary">calendar_today</span>
</div>
<input class="main-index-input-01" id="startDate" name="checkIn" placeholder="날짜 선택" type="date" required/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="stack-gap-1-5">
<label class="label-caps-xs" for="endDate">오는 날</label>
<div class="fx-group-rel">
<div class="input-icon-left">
<span class="icon-ms-muted-focus-primary">event</span>
</div>
<input class="main-index-input-01" id="endDate" name="checkOut" placeholder="날짜 선택" type="date" required/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="main-index-div-08">
<div class="main-index-div-05">
<label class="label-caps-xs" for="guests">인원수</label>
<div class="fx-group-rel">
<div class="input-icon-left">
<span class="icon-ms-muted-focus-primary">group</span>
</div>
<select class="main-index-select-01" id="guests" name="guests">
<option value="1">성인 1명</option>
<option selected="" value="2">성인 2명</option>
<option value="3">성인 3명</option>
<option value="4">성인 4명</option>
<option value="group">단체 (5명 이상)</option>
</select>
<div class="main-index-div-06">
<span class="icon-ms-muted">expand_more</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-full-util">
<button class="fx-group-cta-primary" type="submit">
<span class="icon-ms-hover-pulse">search</span>
                            탐색하기
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
</form>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<main class="page-main-wrap-lg">
<div class="main-index-div-10">
<div>
<h2 class="main-index-h2-01">지금 가장 인기 있는 여행지</h2>
<p class="main-index-p-02">다른 여행자들이 많이 찾는 핫플레이스를 구경해보세요.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="main-index-div-11">
<div class="fx-feature-card-rowspan">
<img alt="Jeju Island" class="media-cover-zoom110-slow" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuADHVQJAyP6Efzppz6Bk1NtK60TjlP-LHFJK4ZwyG5scL4rL18NiKuOb66dg1kWaOx9dDhMwPAIN-8SxETxHpVo1JP9o33cKynOUSRbvAYGibmAnfVps1mrhyHvWKpzcoG46WU9mwQcjRODGwtQ74QtyJjvTrEATQkZaHTE37v2J64sp_r817NIMf7dHpNZdt5j8HgVX_eVbMKDkjUCxA-qtJ9cx0YhMbMn-L3OJxYBrFPPCaq2G75rC0JDuLoyeAQ1IpoKpU9tz7E"/>
<div class="main-index-div-12">
<div class="hover-slide-up">
<span class="badge-inline-primary-soft">인기 급상승</span>
<h3 class="main-index-h3-01">제주 서귀포의 낭만</h3>
<p class="main-index-p-03">에메랄드빛 바다와 함께하는 완벽한 휴식. 프라이빗 풀빌라와 감성 카페 투어를 즐겨보세요.</p>
<div class="main-index-div-13">
<span class="text-lg-base">₩185,000부터</span>
<span class="main-index-span-03">/ 1박</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="media-card">
<img alt="Seoul City" class="media-cover-zoom110-slow" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCsgDVjZ5-BZYHQdxJwLWDgdIgpzdo0hRUbUFXRFQy6NzcEBViLC35AbA4EIrbsLG7SHO8KHoaifm1H6uxwGorUQWt2E9iF7InuijW-HqfmDJs18F8k_bG_JH8ZyuGt0NDiRH_RuAc18dfGUtiV_O-DT1dJ6b2kOyR-4xn65jBxbuErqsrTKxLWb2egoTe9P1Y_P6fpfwCaz6nyFyy5fy6DPItpMAPMdKCf3OqqymI4XB4jOQ-i0MoCR32KIWw1EIc1aib_tm0ZLTA"/>
<div class="media-card-overlay">
